on Logging\nFor security and moderation purposes, we log your IP address at registration and at each connection.\n\n4. Limitation of Liability\nThe platform is provided on an \"AS IS\" basis. We are not liable for damages resulting from your use of the service.\n\n5. Moderation & Termination\nAdministrators reserve the right to remove content, rename accounts, or terminate accounts found in violation of these Terms."
